  <TITLE>The First American Theatre</TITLE>
  <META NAME="keywords" CONTENT="american theatre, williamsburg, Tony Aston, Hallams, Benjamin Colman, Gustavus Vasa, Mat Medley, Samuel Sewall, William Levingston, Charles Stagg">
  <META NAME="description" CONTENT="Bitter Puritanical opposition to plays and play-acting. Severe laws passed prohibiting stage entertainment of any kind. Earliest records of theatrical performance in America. Tony Aston, the first actor to appear in New York. Performance in Boston causes a riot. First theatre in America built in Williamsburg, VA.">
